  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to support the strengthening of capital markets and diversification of the financial sector in Turkey. It will identify key issues preventing the development of Finance Sukuk markets, which will help strengthen the ties between London and Istanbul in non-bank financial sectors and create opportunities for longer term UK financial services&apos; sector involvement.</narrative>
